<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-41cc8b4bfb1ce7901a2976904f55cc858d8ffc37">The Glaive of Pain (E:45, L:3) (9d6) (+0,+30)</h2>
<em>The massive chopper that crowns this glaive glows blood-red and black; fell spells of annihilation swirl and dance as you swing death's myrmidon down.</em> <p>
It is <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Spoilers_2fSentient_20Weapons"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">sentient</a>. It can be wielded two-handed. It drains mana. 
</p>
